description:
Given an array of strings arr[] and an integer k. Find top k maximum occurring strings.

Return the strings sorted in descending order by their frequency. And sort the strings with the same frequency lexicographically.
Constraints:
1 <= N <= 10^5
1 <= arr[i].length <=10

1 <= K <= Number of unique strings in arr[]
title: K maximum occurring strings

default_testcase.input:
1
6 2
ab a ac ds ab a
